(524, 14, '_su_description', 'Our expertise in freight forwarding ensures the best possible results for all parties involved in the transportation process. Call us and see for yourself.'),
(525, 73, '_su_description', 'Our carriers offer customized solutions to bridge various gaps in transportation needs, connecting various modes for better speed, efficiency, and quality.'),
(526, 11, '_su_description', 'With a company culture that empowers, every team member contributes to a network of connections built on trust. Find a promising career with us.'),
(527, 71, '_su_description', 'We can find the most efficient way to transport your cargo, whether you have a smaller or larger volume, seasonal demands, or special project requirements.'),
(528, 81, '_su_description', 'Whether we work with carriers and providers or count on us as a standalone service group, we help you make informed choices in every step of the way.'),
(529, 79, '_su_description', 'Global Logistics Group – GLG allows you to tap into our data-driven supply chain networks to specifically meet your target goals in every shipping project.'),
(530, 225, '_su_description', 'Our brokers maintain constant communication with carriers around the clock to ensure that loads are picked up and dropped without any problems. '),
(531, 13, '_su_description', 'Our expertise in freight brokerage and logistics throughout the USA and Canada offers our clients a wide range of safe and dependable transport options.'),
(532, 40, '_su_description', 'Our freight brokerage experts would love to discuss your needs and inquiries. Count on our expertise in freight forwarding for the best possible results.'),
