(8, 1, '2019-08-14 08:57:04', '2019-08-14 08:57:04', 'Move your freight any time and anywhere with our carrier network. Global Logistics Group - GLG has forged strong business bonds with numerous reliable shippers thanks to our centralized marketplace. Now you don’t have to juggle capacity, rate fluctuations, and services. Find the right match for you!\r\n\r\n<a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'trucking-logistics-get-set-up\']\" class=\"nh_a\">Get Set Up</a>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"shipping-con\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"shipping-row\">\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=\'templateurl\']/images/thumbnails/thumb-9624180.jpg\" alt=\"Trailer truck on highway \" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<h3>Dry Van</h3>\r\n<p>We offer both 48′ and 53′ capacity dry vans that can carry various types of shipment, including food and beverage, machinery, and even hazardous materials. This makes a great 3PL partner for many industries.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"shipping-row\">\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<h3>Temp Controlled</h3>\r\n<p>We know how important it is to get the right carrier for refrigerated transportation. Count on us to match your due diligence on all carriers, ensuring the most secure transportation of perishable and refrigerated loads.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=\'templateurl\']/images/thumbnails/thumb-100318679.jpg\" alt=\"blue semi truck\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"shipping-row\">\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=\'templateurl\']/images/thumbnails/thumb-79875064.jpg\" alt=\"powerful red big rig semi truck with flat bed\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<h3>Flatbed</h3>\r\n<p>Our partner carriers of flatbed trucks that offer various capacities. Utilize them for step-deck, drop-deck, and even flatbed less-than-truckload transport.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"shipping-row\">\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<h3>LTL - Less Than a Truckload</h3>\r\n<p>We provide account-specific pricing, expedited LTL, white-glove services, and more. This is thanks to our network of connections with various common and non-common carriers in the LTL industry.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=\'templateurl\']/images/thumbnails/thumb_588889151.jpg\" alt=\"The forklift in the big warehouse on blurred background\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"shipping-row\">\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=\'templateurl\']/images/thumbnails/thumb_1164027223.jpg\" alt=\"Freight transportation\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<h3>Dedicated Service/Capacity</h3>\r\n<p>Our dedicated carrier partners allow us to provide a consistent quality of shipping coordination. You can count on us to offer consistent transportation solutions for both ends of the logistics process 365 days a year.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"shipping-row\">\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<h3>Expedited</h3>\r\n<p>For quick deliveries, count on us. We offer expedited pricing and capacity in a matter of minutes. Whether it’s through team truckloads, cargo vans, straight trucking, or even air, our specialists will provide on-time delivery and real-time monitoring.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"shipping-col\">\r\n<figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=\'templateurl\']/images/thumbnails/thumb_625771727.jpg\" alt=\"Packages delivery, packaging service and parcels transportation system concept\" /></figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>', 'Shippers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trucking-logistics-shippers', '', '', '2019-11-25 17:06:44', '2019-11-25 17:06:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost/august/globallogistics/?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(9, 1, '2019-08-14 08:57:12', '2019-08-14 08:57:12', '<div class=\"about-us-top\">\r\n<figure><img class=\"thumb_right_dr\" src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/img-our-mission.jpg\" alt=\"group of male worker smiling\" /></figure>\r\nGlobal Logistics Group - GLG is one of the fastest growing third-party logistics providers in the transportation industry. We offer the latest equipment, workforce, and expertise as a trusted trucking logistics company and freight broker in Stafford, Virginia.\r\n\r\nOur team of experts can identify the right transport solutions for any destination to the size, weight, or mode. If you’re transporting domestic shipments within North America, our local market experts draw on our range of resources for ground and air expedited transportation.\r\n<div id=\"mission\" class=\"nh_m\">\r\n<h5>Our Mission <span>Statement</span></h5>\r\nOur mission is to deliver quality transportation services at fair and affordable rates. Unlike many transportation companies today, we maintain pride in what we do. Our company policies are built on common courtesy and the Golden Rule, not just the bare minimum set by state and national logistics standards. We will always treat your freight as if it was ours.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"clearme\"><strong>Why Choose GLG?</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"faq\">\r\n<h6 id=\"nh_1\">Shipping Anywhere in America</h6>\r\n<div>We mobilize a dynamic network of shippers and carriers prepared to deliver any kind of shipment intact and on time.</div>\r\n<h6 id=\"nh_2\">The Best Service Always Guaranteed</h6>\r\n<div>Our experts provide custom solutions that meet every client’s unique transport requirements. Customer satisfaction is always our priority.</div>\r\n<h6 id=\"nh_3\">Effective Logistics Solutions</h6>\r\n<div>We always maintain the highest standards of quality from the pick-up to the drop-off. We don’t waste your time or your money.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nIf you want to learn more, talk to us at 703-552-8753. Our representatives are waiting to address your inquiries.', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'freight-broker-in-stafford-virginia', '', '', '2019-11-25 10:52:50', '2019-11-25 10:52:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/august/globallogistics/?page_id=9', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(10, 1, '2019-08-14 08:56:37', '2019-08-14 08:56:37', 'Send your questions, concerns, and suggestions by filling out this form now.\r\n\r\n[form src=\"contactForm\"]', 'Contact Us', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trucking-logistics-contact-us', '', '', '2019-11-22 23:35:16', '2019-11-22 23:35:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/august/globallogistics/?page_id=10', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(11, 1, '2019-08-14 08:56:41', '2019-08-14 08:56:41', 'Are you interested in a promising logistics career? Take this opportunity and join Global Logistics Group - GLG. Send an application using this form.\r\n\r\n[form src=\"ApplicationForm\"]', 'Job / Careers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trucking-logistics-job-or-careers', '', '', '2019-10-17 19:27:43', '2019-10-17 19:27:43', '', 0, 'http://localhost/august/globallogistics/?page_id=11', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(12, 1, '2019-08-14 08:56:51', '2019-08-14 08:56:51', 'Global Logistics Group - GLG uses state-of-the-art technology to keep in touch with a wide network of freight carriers. Our specialists help clients choose from an extensive number of shipments per day. By choosing us as your logistics partner, you can work with carriers that cater to various industries and freight types. Book the best loads now!\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"carr_heading\">RELIABILITY GUARANTEED</h2>\r\nGlobal Logistics Group - GLG never falters in its quality in every step of the freight transport process. As a top-of-the-line freight broker, we make sure every carrier carries the right load all the time, whatever the equipment type. Our dedicated logistics team provides support even after hours.\r\n\r\nCount on us for:\r\n<div class=\"carrier_con\">\r\n<section class=\"grow\"> \r\n<h2><a href=\"javascript:;\"><span>Access to a diverse selection of loads</span></a></h2>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"grow\"> \r\n<h2><a href=\"freight-of-all-types-and-commodities\"><span>Freight of all types and commodities</span></a></h2>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"grow\">\r\n<h2><a href=\"#options\"><span>Convenient payment options</span></a></h2>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"grow\"> \r\n<h2><a href=\"dedicated-carrier-relations\"><span>Dedicated carrier relations</span></a></h2>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"grow\">\r\n<h2><a href=\"round-the-clock-assistance\"><span>Round-the-clock assistance</span></a></h2>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n<section class=\"grow\">\r\n<h2><a href=\"javascript:;\"><span>Perfectly tailored shipment</span></a></h2>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"options\"></div>\r\n\r\n<strong>Payment Options</strong>\r\n\r\nQuick Pay Option:\r\n<ul class=\"bullet col2\">\r\n  <li>24 Hours\r\n  <li>7 days\r\n  <li>21 days (no fee)\r\n  <li>EFS Fuel Advance\r\n  <li>ACH Direct Deposit\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[form src=\"carriersForm\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'trucking-logistics-get-set-up\']\" class=\"nh_a\">Get Set Up</a>', 'Carriers', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trucking-logistics-carriers', '', '', '2019-10-17 19:27:03', '2019-10-17 19:27:03', '', 0, 'http://localhost/august/globallogistics/?page_id=12', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(13, 1, '2019-08-14 08:57:18', '2019-08-14 08:57:18', 'Whenever you need to deliver your shipment to locations across the US, count on Global Logistics Group - GLG. Our expertise in freight brokerage and logistics throughout the USA and Canada offers our clients a wide range of safe and dependable transport options. \r\n\r\nTime-sensitive and cost-sensitive, we support your asset management decision through optimal supply chain solutions. As a freight broker in Stafford, Virginia, we can survey your locations to determine the best possible custom pick-up solutions for each facility, regardless of size, weight, or mode.\r\n\r\n<strong>Count on us for:</strong>\r\n<div class=\"serv_list\">\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/thumb-94432044.jpg\" alt=\"Red big rig modern shiny semi-truck with white dry van trailer\" ><figcaption><a href=\"full-truckload\"><span>Full Truckload</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n    <li><figure><img src=\"[contenturl type=templateurl]/images/thumbnails/thumb-660736690.jpg\" alt=\"trailer in a broad daylight\" ><figcaption><a href=\"less-than-truckload\"><span>Less Than Truckload</span></a></figcaption></figure></li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\nDial 703-552-8753 to learn more.', 'Services', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'trucking-logistics-services', '', '', '2019-10-10 09:35:27', '2019-10-10 09:35:27', '', 0, 'http://localhost/august/globallogistics/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
