(142, 1, '2019-08-19 07:53:53', '2019-08-19 07:53:53', 'Global Logistics Group - GLG uses state-of-the-art technology to keep in touch with a wide network of freight carriers. Our specialists help clients choose from an extensive number of shipments per day. By choosing us as your logistics partner, you can work with carriers that cater to various industries and freight types. Book the best loads now!\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"carr_heading\">RELIABILITY GUARANTEED</h2>\r\nGlobal Logistics Group - GLG never falters in its quality in every step of the freight transport process. As a top-of-the-line freight broker, we make sure every carrier carries the right load all the time, whatever the equipment type. Our dedicated logistics team provides support even after hours.\r\n\r\nCount on us for:\r\n<ul class=\"bullet\">\r\n<li>Access to a diverse selection of loads</li>\r\n<li>Freight of all types and commodities</li>\r\n<li>Convenient payment options</li>\r\n<li>Dedicated carrier relations between the USA and Canada</li>\r\n<li>Round-the-clock assistance every day of the year</li>\r\n<li>Perfectly tailored shipment solutions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<strong>Payment Options</strong>\r\n\r\nQuick Pay Option:\r\n<ul class=\"bullet\">\r\n  <li>24 Hours</li>\r\n  <li>7 days</li>\r\n  <li>21 days (no fee)</li>\r\n  <li>EFS Fuel Advance</li>\r\n  <li>ACH Direct Deposit</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n[form src=\"carriersForm\"]\r\n\r\n<a href=\"[contenturl type=\'siteurl\' page=\'trucking-logistics-get-a-quote\']\" class=\"nh_a\">Get a Quote</a>', 'Carriers', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '12-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-19 07:53:53', '2019-08-19 07:53:53', '', 12, 'https://web4.proweaverlinks.com/globallogistics/12-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(144, 1, '2019-08-19 08:03:56', '2019-08-19 08:03:56', 'Global Logistics Group - GLG knows that inefficiency harms quality. To make sure that no amount of time or resources goes wasted, we rely on the latest data processing technology.\r\n\r\nWe don’t wait on simple load boards but precise, real-time results. Using refined algorithms, we match every carrier with the right load at the right price every time. Never worry about lost mileage or missed deadlines. Expect consistent service standards when you choose us as your 3PL partner. \r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"carr_heading\">24/7 Monitoring</h3>\r\nWorried about poor safety scores, low authority status, or lack of insurance? Our real-time monitoring system helps us vet the carriers we work with to give you the transport solution you require. Optimizing your operations is always our central priority.\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"carr_heading\">Key Analytics</h3\r\nNo one succeeds with guesswork. To meet your supply chain needs, we provide you with data-driven solutions by running customized KPIs (Key Performance Indicators) and reports. We analyze the results of your performance to determine the best steps for optimization.\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"carr_heading\">EDI</h3\r\nOur Electronic Data Interchange (EDI) system is primed to perform various processes like carrier assignment, order entry, and accounting in a streamlined fashion. This prevents errors that will hold back your operations and boost your productivity.\r\n\r\nLearn more by calling 703-552-8753. ', 'Technology', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '134-revision-v1', '', '', '2019-08-19 08:03:56', '2019-08-19 08:03:56', '', 134, 'https://web4.proweaverlinks.com/globallogistics/134-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
