(297, 2, '2019-10-21 01:26:29', '2019-10-21 01:26:29', '<img src=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/reasons-you-need-a-3pl-provider.jpg\" alt=\"Reasons You Need a 3PL Provider\" width=\"668\" height=\"446\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-302\" />\r\n\r\nA 3PL, or third-party logistics, is an outsourced service that organizes delivery, dispatch, and storage of <a href=\"https://www.marineinsight.com/know-more/16-types-of-container-units-and-designs-for-shipping-cargo/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">cargo</a> and merchandise. They have proven themselves very useful for manufacturing companies and suppliers. \r\n\r\nAre you having trouble with your freightage? Do you think you need help making <a href=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">freight forwarding in Canada</a> easier? If you answered yes, then you’re on the right track. Here are a few other reasons why you need a 3PL provider.\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"bullet\">\r\n<li><strong>Shipment varies in type and quantity</strong>\r\n\r\nYou just need a <a href=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/trucking-logistics-shippers\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">trucking company in Virginia</a> today, but tomorrow you might need a different carrier. If the cargo is going to be different every time, then you would need to source new transportation services too. Save some time and just have one freight broker do all these for you. \r\n</li>\r\n\r\n<li><strong>Your products need to cross a border </strong>\r\n\r\nInternational shipping can be difficult, mainly because of customs requirements and other credentials. If you get a <a href=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/freight-broker-in-stafford-virginia\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">freight broker in Stafford, Virginia</a>, like Global Logistics Group - GLG , you no longer have to worry about these things. They have an expansive network and resource that can cater to your s