(343, 2, '2019-12-11 03:20:15', '2019-12-11 03:20:15', '<img src=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/role-of-freight-brokers-in-supply-chain-management.jpg\" alt=\"Role of Freight Brokers in Supply Chain Management\" width=\"668\" height=\"446\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-344\" />\r\n\r\nEvery goods or product goes through a process. Starting with the acquisition of raw materials, manufacturing, quality checking, and then distributing. It\'s the whole process every product goes through, from production to consumption. \r\n \r\n<a href=\"https://hardluckcastle.com/importance-of-freight-brokers/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Freight brokers</a> play an important role in transporting a product from its point of origin, the factory or production site, to the customers. Depending on your supply chain needs, a <a href=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/freight-broker-in-stafford-virginia\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">freight broker in Stafford, Virginia</a>, can help you run your business smoothly. If you find the right broker, you can save a lot of money and sustain the business.\r\n\r\nGlobal Logistics Group - GLG is an expert on <a href=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">freight forwarding in Canada</a>. We transport all kinds of goods in varying quantities. We take pride in our professional service and in arranging a fast and convenient haul, shipment, and delivery. \r\n\r\nFor your local delivery needs, we can arrange a <a href=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/trucking-logistics-shippers\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">trucking company in Virginia</a> to bring your goods to stores and homes. We only connect with high-quality transportation services and uphold high standards when it comes to shipment. Through us, you can guarantee efficient and cost-efficient shipment.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://www.glgfreight.com/trucking-logistics-contact-us\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Reach out</a> to us if you need a broker who can handle any kind of shipment for your supply chain needs. We’d be happy to discuss the options we have for you.\r\n\r\n\r\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\r\n{\r\n\"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\r\n\"@type\": \"NewsArticle\",\r\n\"mainEntityOfPage\": {\r\n\"@type\": \"WebPage\",\r\n\"@id\": \"http://www.glgfreight.com/role-of-freight-brokers-in-supply-chain-management\"\r\n},\r\n\"headline\": \"Role of Freight Brokers in Supply Chain Management\",\r\n\"image\": [\r\n\"http://www.glgfreight.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/role-of-freight-brokers-in-supply-chain-management.jpg\",\r\n\"http://www.glgfreight.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/role-of-freight-brokers-in-supply-chain-management-300x200.jpg\",\r\n\"http://www.glgfreight.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/role-of-freight-brokers-in-supply-chain-management-150x150.jpg\"\r\n],\r\n\"datePublished\": \"2019-12-11\",\r\n\"dateModified\": \"2019-12-11\",\r\n\"author\": {\r\n\"@type\": \"Person\",\r\n\"name\": \"Louise Savioe\"\r\n},\r\n\"publisher\": {\r\n\"@type\": \"Organization\",\r\n\"name\": \"Global Logistics Group - GLG\",\r\n\"logo\": {\r\n\"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\r\n\"url\": \"http://www.glgfreight.com/wp-content/themes/globallogistics/images/main-logo.png\"\r\n}\r\n},\r\n\"description\": \"Freight brokers play an important role in transporting a product from its point of origin, the factory or production site, to the customers.\"\r\n}\r\n</script>', 'Role of Freight Brokers in Supply Chain Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'role-of-freight-brokers-in-supply-chain-management', '', '', '2019-12-11 07:15:03', '2019-12-11 07:15:03', '', 0, 'http://www.glgfreight.com/?p=343', 0, 'post', '', 0),
